Plexium maintains a persistent wiki in `.wiki/` that agents keep up to date.

## Before code changes
- Read `.wiki/_schema.md` for the wiki constitution and ownership rules
- Read `.wiki/_index.md` for orientation
- Read relevant `.wiki/modules/*.md` pages for your work area

## After code changes
- Update affected wiki pages in `.wiki/`
- Never modify pages with `ownership: human-authored`
- Add an entry to `.wiki/_log.md`

